page.title: 05HOUSES IN CATTERLINE
page.content: There are twenty nine houses in Catterline village and some people live on farms round about. On the day I am writing this, a builder has started building seven new houses. Three people live down at the old mill. There is a holiday house which lots of people go to in the summer. There is an old cottage on a cliff, which has been turned into an artist's studio but it was built for a watch house for smugglers. At the front of the village three old cottages have been turned into the Creel Inn, a bar where you can get a meal. Catterline is a nice place and everyone likes it.
